  "leavePolicy": "<h2><strong><u>Leave Application Policy</u></strong></h2><h3></h3><h3><strong>1. Introduction</strong></h3><p>This document outlines the leave application policy for all employees. Adherence to this policy is mandatory.</p><h3></h3><h3><strong>2. Types of Leave</strong></h3><p>Our company provides the following types of leave:</p><ul><li>Annual Leave: Employees are entitled to 20 days of annual leave.</li><li>Sick Leave: Employees are entitled to 10 days of sick leave per year.</li><li>Casual Leave: Employees can avail up to 7 days of casual leave.</li></ul><h3></h3><h3><strong>3. Application Process</strong></h3><p>The leave application process is as follows:</p><ul><li>Submit a leave application form at least 5 days in advance.</li><li>Ensure that your leave does not clash with critical project timelines.</li><li>Obtain approval from your immediate supervisor.</li></ul><h3></h3><h3><strong>4. Leave Approval</strong></h3><p>All leave requests are subject to approval based on business requirements and staffing levels.</p><p></p><h3><strong>5. Contact Information</strong></h3><p>If you have any questions regarding the leave policy, please contact the HR department at hr@company.com.</p><p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>"
}

